						p.ar-text In this example, we're going to practice digging into Obscurity's coat of gadgets. You can follow along below or check out an animated tutorial by using the button controls! 
						br
						p.ar-text Static Grenade is a Utility card available in OBSCURITY's deck. Played by itself, Static Grenades sits in play waiting for you to VANISH it. When you VANISH Static Grenades, it deals 1 damage to each opponent and their Utilities. 
						br
						p.ar-text X-Ray Spex is a Utility card available in OBSCURITY's deck. Played by itself, X-Ray Spex sits in play waiting for you to VANISH it. When you VANISH X-Ray Spex, you may choose to play an Action card from your hand for free.
						br
						p.ar-text As you can see by the sub-type underneath the card titles, both Static Grenade and X-Ray Spex are Gadgets. That means that OBSCURITY can VANISH Static Grenades to turn it upside-down. Face-down Utilities are hidden from all players until they are turned face-up and using VANISH on face-down Gadgets will turn them face-up.
						br
						p.ar-text Both Static Grenades and X-Ray Spex have abilities that trigger each time you VANISH them. This ability will fire every time you VANISH the card, regardless whether it is face-up or face-down. There is no limit for the number of times you are able to VANISH a given Utility per turn, meaning that each of these Gadgets could fire 3 times or more per turn!
