						br
						p.ar-text Vibro-Knuckle Dusters is a Utility card available in OBSCURITY's deck. Played by itself, Vibro-Knuckle Dusters sits in play waiting for you to VANISH it. When you do VANISH Vibro-Knuckle Dusters, you may play the top card of your deck for free.
						br
						p.ar-text Let's say your turn begins with a copy of Vibro-Knuckle Dusters in play face-down. Since it is face-down, you won't be able to attack with Vibro-Knuckle Duster's until you turn it face-up. 
						br
						p.ar-text Next, let's play a copy of Crack Shot. Crack Shot is an Action card available in OBSCURITY's deck. Many of OBSCURITY's Actions give you the choice of choosing between multiple options. Played by itself, Crack Shot lets you deal 2 damage to any target or VANISH one of your Gadgets.
						br
						p.ar-text Crack Shot gives us the choice of dealing 2 damage to any target or Vanishing our Vibro-Knuckle Dusters. Turning our Gadget face-up would let us attack and allows us to play the top card of your deck for free thanks to the Dusters' bonus ability! It's entirely possible we find another copy of Crack Shot or another set of Knuckle Dusters!
